data.description: Discover the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience with this charming mobile home nestled on a sprawling 6.99-acre lot. Escape the hustle and bustle of city life and embrace a serene country lifestyle, while still enjoying easy access to amenities. This property offers ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, or even the possibility of building. Property also features a Separate living quarters with a comfortable bedroom, fully equipped kitchenette, bathroom, and a cozy living area.  Perfect for accommodating guests, extended family, or even as a rental opportunity. Pond, Natural spring on property! Roof 2017, AC 2013. Schedule your showing today! *Agents see remarks and directions*
